    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An &quot;indie gem&quot; - a unique game based on the novel by screenwriter, Jake Stephen Jackson - brought to life in a brand new experience. Sven, Kate and Chariot are characters you will never forget as they join you on your quest throughout the Milky Way Galaxy to bring an end to the Progenitor War.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New!</strong> For game preservation purposes, we've updated the game to include the 'Director's Cut' materials, that was cut from the planned Remaster before we released REMAKE. Director's Cut is future proofed to run on Windows 11 24H2 and beyond by using Voodoo wrapper and we have replaced the incompatible engine that the original game was using before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With whole new areas and cinematic animated backdrops that resemble the Remake, this is the definitive version of The Dawning Clocks of Time (Original).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730630/extras/fecf508c932a67f7596d4810eefdfabb.avif?t=1745615928\" width=660 height=1200 /></span></p>",
